{
  "stem": "21013.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was in different groups, summer camps, and always through the Social Democratic Party.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father felt it was important that I mingle with the worker's children, rather than just the elite.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] those were the groups and we were indoctrinated that war is a terrible thing and that we should fight against it, and let the big shots fight among themselves and not involve the people, because we suffered so much in the war.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were taught that the Versailles Treaty was very unfair, which of course history has proven so.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were all extremely politically aware, all the children, like I said, from age 6 on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know football scores.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we knew about politics.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I had close friends in my building where I lived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a group of children that played in this courtyard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all but two became ardent Nazis.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the terrible thing was when Hitler marched into Austria, they brought out their uniforms.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had uniforms.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And these young boys and girls would spit on me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were my best friends, and wouldn't talk to me and wouldn't-- like I said, spit at me and throw stones and it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what could you do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First you tried to talk to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then your parents tell you that if you talk back, you're going to get killed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You-- they want to-- in the-- in the parks, there were benches where you couldn't sit.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the street, you couldn't take certain forms of transportation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it goes right to the very center of your being.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I saw it even before Hitler marched into Austria, long before.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
